            "title": "盤中速報 - 同欣電(6271)股價拉至漲停，漲停價140.5元，成交6,845張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>同欣電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6271:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6271\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6271-TW</a>)22日12:19上漲12.5元，股價漲停報140.5元，委買42張、委賣412張，成交6,845張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為影像產品。混合積體電路模組。陶瓷電路板。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>同欣電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6271:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6271\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6271-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌1.92%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.98%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,335 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,687 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+31 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-383 張</li> <li>融資增減：-361 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
